{"tid":1292142,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(重新po)*突發!!* 發夢13號旺角有free hug","createTime":"2019-07-07T07:31:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-10T10:40:44.000Z","uid":253325,"like":5,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"81f8ed6fd7b1c6ed8bb6d78335920fac072f7767","tid":1292142,"uid":253325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T07:31:11.000Z","msg":"最近，社會有好多鬱悶的氣氛，作為同路人，我哋好明白大家的感受，所以想為大家打打氣，就發夢搞個free hug活動，當日除咗有free hug，仲會派傳單同傾談服務 (自行決定)<br />\n<br />\n雖然作用未必好大，但我哋覺得覺得擁抱勝過千言萬語!<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">發夢宗旨</span></span><br />\n我地嘅宗旨係需要得到雙方同意先可以free hug<br />\n如有一方不同意，可拒絕<br />\n盡量同性free hug，以免不必要的衝突<br />\n切記要安全至上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n時間: 7月13號2:30-6:00<br />\n地點: 旺角行人天橋<br />\n 集合時間: 下午2:00 旺角B出大堂<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">發夢抱抱備註</span></div><br />\n- 如怕羞或被影，建議戴個口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n- 背囊或大容量的袋 (裝水，衣物，傳單)<br />\n- 當日以純色輕便衣服為主<br />\n- 更換衣物 (方便活動完結時換，唔使着住件臭汗衫走<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n(如有其他意見再加<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">發夢抱抱注意</span></div><br />\n- 如有撐狗人士/狗圍或挑機，盡量勿理論，勿口角<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n- 有唔對路就走為上着轉地方繼續<br />\n(保護絲打優先，絲打走先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00acba529b39379ec63e5f73d45b603d24482919","tid":1292142,"uid":229269,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T07:32:41.000Z","msg":"支持<br />\n留名跟進<img src=\"/assets/faces/l